<%= render 'shared/navbar' %>

<div class="section cards">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="twelve columns">
                <h2 class="homepage-h2" style="margin-bottom: 4rem;">
                    Augment your team's capacity with a skilled volunteer.
                </h2>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="spacer"></div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="four columns">
                <h3>
                    1. Post a project
                </h3>
                <p class="dark-paragraph">
                    Describe a challenge or task that your organization needs help with. Volunteer projects can be as small as a quick phone call, or as large as a multi-week effort.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="four columns">
                <h3>
                    2. Connect with volunteers
                </h3>
                <p class="dark-paragraph">
                    Once posted, your project will be visible to hundreds of volunteers. If a volunteer is intersted in your project, they will introduce themselves.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="four columns">
                <h3>
                    3. Choose the right volunteer
                </h3>
                <p class="dark-paragraph">
                    You'll be able to review each candidate by chatting with them and viewing their past work. You get to choose which volunteer you'd like to work with.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="spacer"></div>
        <div class="spacer"></div>

        <div class="row" style="background-color: #2A2F2F;">
            <div class="two-cards columns">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3>
                            Have questions?
                        </h3>
                        <div class="divider"></div>
                        <p>
                            If you have any questions about how the platform works, don't hesitate to reach out and say hello!
                        </p>
                        <%= mail_to "team@project501.com", "Email Us", target: "_blank", class: "button-secondary" %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="two-cards columns">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3>
                            Ready to get started?
                        </h3>
                        <div class="divider"></div>
                        <p>
                            Sign up to post a project, connect with skilled volunteers, and propel your organization forward.
                        </p>
                        <%= link_to "Get Started", new_organization_path, class: "button-primary"%>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="spacer"></div>
        <div class="spacer"></div>
        <div class="spacer"></div>
        <div class="spacer"></div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="twelve columns">
                <h2 class="homepage-h2" style="margin-bottom: 4rem;">
                    What do you need help with?
                </h2>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="three-cards columns">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3>
                            Design
                        </h3>
                        <div class="divider"></div>
                        <p>
                            Design a website, app, or your next set of marketing materials.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="three-cards columns">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3>
                            Web Development
                        </h3>
                        <div class="divider"></div>
                        <p>
                            Step into 2017 with a fast, mobile responsive website.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="three-cards columns">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3>
                            Marketing
                        </h3>
                        <div class="divider"></div>
                        <p>
                            Execute on a strategy to reach your supporters.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="three-cards columns">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3>
                            Strategy
                        </h3>
                        <div class="divider"></div>
                        <p>
                            Navigate a path to making the most impact possible.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="three-cards columns">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3>
                            Fundraising
                        </h3>
                        <div class="divider"></div>
                        <p>
                            Drum up the finances you need to continue operating.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="three-cards columns">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3>
                            Content Production
                        </h3>
                        <div class="divider"></div>
                        <p>
                            Produce an inspiring video to communicate your mission.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="spacer"></div>
        <div class="spacer"></div>
        <div class="spacer"></div>
        <div class="spacer"></div>

    </div>

    <div class="spacer"></div>
    <div class="spacer"></div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="twelve columns">
            <h3 class="centered-text">
                Interested in learning more about Project 501? <%= mail_to "team@project501.com", "Email Us", target: "_blank", class: "inline-link" %> to setup a demo of the platform.
            </h3>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="marketing-footer">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row" style="overflow: hidden;">
            <div class="six columns">
                <h3>
                    Made with üê∂ in Cambridge, MA.
                </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="six columns">
                <div class="right">
                    <h3>
                        <%= mail_to "team@project501.com", "Contact Us", target: "_blank" %>
                    </h3>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
